  "title": "HUMAN RESOURCE & ADMINISTRATION MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Mega Collective:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Looking to work in an exciting and rewarding hospitality environment? Mega Collective is now hiring! Mega Collective is an established F&amp;B group. Our portfolio consists of various kinds of establishments, including Hub &amp; Spoke Café, Time For Thai, Urbans @ Plaza 8 and Overflow. We offer café-style dining, full service restaurants, bars and food courts.</p>\n<p>Our growing team is filled with energetic, motivated professionals who thrive on change. As a company, we always put people first. If you want to help us create unique, thoughtful concepts while offering top-notch hospitality service, join us today!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Roles &amp; Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>You will be part of the HR team as a HR Manager playing the part of relationship building between stakeholders and employees. You will provide professional advice regarding HR policies, procedures, manpower planning and reward strategies. You will also be involved in projects targeting succession planning and employee engagement.</p>\n<p>• Manage end-to-end recruitment functions<br>\n• Posting &amp; drafting job advertisement via various job portals<br>\n• Administers various human resource plans and procedures<br>\n• Administer work pass applications, renewal, cancellations and other related matters<br>\n• Performs benefits administration and communicates benefits information to employees.<br>\n• Provide support for payroll administration to ensure accuracy<br>\n• Maintains human resource information system records and compile reports from the database.<br>\n• Perform any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>• Diploma or Degree in HR Management/Business Admin<br>\n• Ability to work independently, meet tight deadlines and perform multiple tasks<br>\n• Good organizational capabilities with a keen eye for details</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Employee Benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Increment and Performance Bonus</li>\n  <li>Medical Benefits</li>\n  <li>Annual Leave, PH and many more</li>\n  <li>Staff meal provided</li>\n  <li>Career Progression</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>How to Apply:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>·  Send your Resume and a Headshot to<strong> </strong><a href=\"mailto:hello@megacollectiveco.com\">hello@megacollectiveco.com</a></p>\n<p>·  Insert the title you are applying for in the email Subject</p>\n<p>·  State your Full Name and Age in the application.</p>\n<p>·  Only Singaporeans/Singapore PR need apply.</p>\n<p>Regret to inform you that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted by our consultants.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
